Que.2 - Gas calculation and How to convert Gas to Ether.
Que.3 - Calculator Contract build compile ,  deploy in the Ethereum blockchain.



# 1. Ethereum accounts

1. EOAs Externally owned accounts  for example metamask Account

            control by private key      

2. CA (Contract Accounts )

       Control By code 




# 2. Gas fee âž– Calculation

Gas  price per unit = 100 Gwei 

transaction gas limit = 21000

Total fee = gas price per unit * Gas limit =  2100000 Gwei   =  0.0021 ETH

Notes:-   1 Gwei = 10^9




# 3. Calculator Contract build and deploy in the Ethereum blockchain.

Example:-

// SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT

pragma solidity ^0.8.0;

contract Calculator{

    uint public result;

    function add(uint256 a , uint256 b ) public 
    {
        result = a+b;

    }

     function subtract(uint256 a , uint256 b ) public 
    {
        result = a-b;
        
    }

     function multiply(uint256 a , uint256 b ) public 
    {
        result = a*b;
        
    }

     function divide(uint256 a , uint256 b ) public 
    {
        result = a/b;
        
    }
}
